# Setup guide

Setup code on your machine

git clone <url>

git checkout -b <name_of_branch>


Insde the project folder

1. Create a virtual environment
2. Activate virtual environment
3. pip install -r requirements.txt
4. Setup up postgres
5. Create a database called ziloshipping
6. Download postactivate file and place it inside <project_folder>/<virtual_env_dorectory>/bin/
7. Activate virtual environment (source env/bin/activate)
8. Activate envorment variables (source env/bin/postactivate)
5. Run migrations
6. Run the code (python manage.py runserver)
